 war-torn countries.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 0aDemocratization. 0aPeace-building. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Peace.2bisacsh1 aEvenson, Kristie D., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aManning, Carrie, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRiese, Sarah, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRoehner, Nora, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311070420440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080478467240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804784672423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804784672.jpg  a978-3-11-070420-4  SUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles